
  Tropius    Grass Type Pokémon

  The bunches of fruit around 
  TROPIUS’s neck are very popular 
  with children.  Tropius 
  loves fruit, and eats it continuously. 
   Apparently, its love for fruit 
  resulted in its own outgrowth 
  of fruit. 
